has dreams like that.

59
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,454
What are you looking for anyway?

60
00:03:06,522 --> 00:03:07,589
The camcorder.

61
00:03:07,657 --> 00:03:09,591
I thought I had it
in the case.

62
00:03:09,659 --> 00:03:12,427
